query:
SELECT 
  total_records,
  COUNT(*) as combinations_count
FROM (
  SELECT 
    countryId,
    serviceId,
    COUNT(*) as total_records
  FROM prices
  GROUP BY countryId, serviceId
) as subquery
GROUP BY total_records
ORDER BY total_records;
